Carlos Alazraki Grossmann (born 1947 in Mexico City) is a Mexican advertising executive.
Alazraki is the founder, president, and CEO of Alazraki & Asociados Publicidad agency and the previous president of the Asociaci√≥n Mexicana de Agencias de Publicidad (AMAP, Mexican Association of Advertising Agencies). He is the son of film director Benito Alazraki and son-in-law of the late Samy Yeroham, owner of Topeka. He is also the father of directory Gary Alazraki.


